OL,3,CTrump warns Iran not to play in 2026
OL,4,CWorld Cup 'for their own life and
OL,5,Csafety'
OL,7,FDonald Trump has warned that Iran's
OL,8,Ffootball team should not come to the
OL,9,FWorld Cup "for their own life and
OL,10,Fsafety".
OL,12,FIn a post on Truth Social on Thursday,
OL,13,Fthe US president wrote: "The Iran
OL,14,FNational Soccer Team is welcome to The
OL,15,FWorld Cup, but I really don't believe
OL,16,Fit is appropriate that they be there,
OL,17,Ffor their own life and safety."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
