OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1773363777
OL,3,CTrump warns Iran not to play in 2026
OL,4,CWorld Cup 'for their own life and
OL,5,Csafety'
OL,7,FTrump's comment comes just days after
OL,8,Ftelling Fifa President Giovanni
OL,9,FInfantino that the team would be
OL,10,Fwelcome, despite the ongoing war in
OL,11,Fthe Middle East.
OL,13,FIn an Instagram post on Tuesday,
OL,14,FInfantino confirmed he had spoken to
OL,15,FTrump about the current situation in
OL,16,FIran.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
