CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1773363777
OL,3,CTrump warns Iran not to play in 2026
OL,4,CWorld Cup 'for their own life and
OL,5,Csafety'
OL,7,FThe FIFA boss said: "During the
OL,8,Fdiscussions, President Trump
OL,9,Freiterated that the Iranian team is,
OL,10,Fof course, welcome to compete in the
OL,11,Ftournament in the United States.
OL,13,F"We all need an event like the Fifa
OL,14,FWorld Cup to bring people together now
OL,15,Fmore than ever, and I sincerely thank
OL,16,Fthe President of the United States for
OL,17,Fhis support, as it shows once again
OL,18,Fthat football unites the world."
