OL,3,CTrump warns Iran not to play in 2026
OL,4,CWorld Cup 'for their own life and
OL,5,Csafety'
OL,7,FThe 2026 World Cup is set to take
OL,8,Fplace in the summer, hosted by the
OL,9,FUSA, Canada and Mexico.
OL,11,FThe US and Israel launched attacks on
OL,12,FIran at the end of February, killing
OL,13,FIran's Supreme leader Ayatollah Ali
OL,14,FKhamenei.
OL,16,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,17,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,18,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,19,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
