OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1773363777
OL,3,CTrump warns Iran not to play in 2026
OL,4,CWorld Cup 'for their own life and
OL,5,Csafety'
OL,7,FIran's Minister of Sports and Youth,
OL,8,FAhmad Donyamali, said in an interview
OL,9,Fwith the IRIB Sports Network on
OL,10,FTuesday that Iran would not be
OL,11,Fpartaking.
OL,13,FDonyamali said: "Given that this
OL,14,Fcorrupt government has assassinated
OL,15,Four leader, under no circumstances do
OL,16,Fwe have the appropriate conditions to
OL,17,Fparticipate in the World Cup.
OL,19,F"Our boys are not safe, and conditions
OL,20,Ffor participation do not exist."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
