PN,31206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1773363777
OL,3,CTrump warns Iran not to play in 2026
OL,4,CWorld Cup 'for their own life and
OL,5,Csafety'
OL,7,FHe added: "Over the past eight or nine
OL,8,Fmonths, two wars have been imposed on
OL,9,Fus and several thousand of our people
OL,10,Fhave been killed and martyred.
OL,11,FTherefore, we definitely do not have
OL,12,Fthe possibility for participation."
OL,14,FIran is currently one of 48 teams in
OL,15,Ftournament and is scheduled to face
OL,16,FNew Zealand on June 15.
OL,18,FThey have not officially withdrawn
OL,19,Ffrom the World Cup.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
